[The reports above highlight an early surge in influenza cases this year [2022], with higher number of cases and deaths being reported. Influenza season generally peaks during January or February, while there has been an unusual increase reported in many countries. Use of masks, social distancing, and hand hygiene practices along with annual influenza vaccination should be promoted, especially among the high-risk population groups. - Mod.UBA

